The paper focuses on the security and privacy issues in edge learning for autonomous vehicles, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses machine learning techniques and communication protocols, which are relevant to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
